The Brandon University Bobcats men’s volleyball team wrapped up its pre-season with a 3-1 (21-25, 25-22, 29-27, 25-15) loss to the University of Montreal Carabins in Winnipeg on Friday afternoon. 
Roy Ching led BU with 17 kills, four blocks and four digs, while Seth Friesen added 12 kills and four digs. Please subscribe to view full article.
